Effect of Exchange Rate Changes: effect of exchange rate on cash cash equivalents restricted cash and restricted cash equivalents including disposal group and discontinued operations

Net Cash from Financing Activities: net cash provided by used in financing activities
Proceeds from Debt: proceeds from issuance of long term debt
proceeds from sale of debt and equity securities
proceeds from repayments of other short term debt
Proceeds from Stock Issuance: proceeds from issuance of common stock
Stock Repurchases: payments for repurchase of common stock

Acquisitions (net of cash acquired): payments to acquire businesses net of cash acquired
Capital Expenditures: payments for proceeds from property plant and equipment
payments to acquire property plant and equipment
Net Cash from Investing Activities: net cash provided by used in investing activities
Other Investing Activities: proceeds from collection of loans receivable
proceeds from divestiture of businesses net of cash divested
Purchases of Investments: payments to acquire equity method investments
Sales and Maturities of Investments: proceeds from maturities prepayments and calls of available for sale securities
proceeds from sale and maturity of other investments
proceeds from sale of available for sale securities

Net Change in Cash: cash cash equivalents restricted cash and restricted cash equivalents period increase decrease including exchange rate effect

Changes in Operating Assets and Liabilit: increase decrease in accounts and other receivables
increase decrease in accounts payable accrued and other operating liabilities
increase decrease in deferred policy acquisition costs
increase decrease in other operating capital net
increase decrease in pharmacy and service costs payable
Deferred Income Taxes: increase decrease in deferred income taxes
Net Cash from Operating Activities: net cash provided by used in operating activities
Other Non-Cash Items: gain loss on sale of business
gains losses on extinguishment of debt
